ource Connections, and was the founding leader of the Search Center of Excellence at Wolters Kluwer.</p>\n<p>Max has over 20 years of experience directing delivery and strategy of large scale applications in various industries, with 10 of those years globally managing large diverse teams to improve search quality to drive results. He has deep practical hands-on technical expertise in search relevance, customer experience, natural language processing, and growing quality-focused culture.</p></div>\n                    \n                </div>\n            </div>\n        \n    \n    </article>\n\n\n                </main>\n            </div>\n            <footer>\n                \n                \n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n    powered by <a href=\"/redirect/?url=https%3A//pretalx.com%3AFZHsiuBcrC2IlEJJu6SMtZpwByWhWO8BK25RGYOfxHY\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">pretalx</a>\n\n\n                \n                    ·\n                    <a href=\"mailto:info@berlinbuzzwords.de\">Contact us</a>\n                \n                \n                    ·\n                    <a href=\"https://plainschwarz.com/imprint-impressum/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Imprint</a>\n                \n                \n                    ·\n                    <a href=\"/redirect/?url=/bbuzz22/privacy%3AWnyyxMlUE8Ir_xskHJ3cgJLVPwKGLFuxM7I0lVTHoWw\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Privacy</a>\n                \n            </footer>\n        </div>\n        \n\n<dialog id=\"lightbox-dialog\" role=\"alertdialog\" aria-labelledby=\"lightbox-label\">\n    <form method=\"dialog\" class=\"modal-card\">\n        <div class=\"modal-card-content\">\n            <figure class=\"text-center text-muted\">\n                <img>\n                <figcaption id=\"lightbox-label\"></figcaption>\n            </figure>\n            <button id=\"lightbox-close\" class=\"btn btn-default btn-xs\" aria-label=\"Close\"><i class=\"fa fa-times\"></i></button>\n        </div>\n    </form>\n</dialog